modName: Alice-Madness Returns Eyes and actually dead black eyes
summary: Woo more A:MR stuff. Why, because I can. Just eyes, but I\'m working on clothes n stuff for other mods :3 It\'s fun and most of em act weird because Skyrim is weird and likes normal irises and pupils.
descriptionHtml:
Alice: Madness Returns and it\'s assets belong to Spicy Horse

Textures courtesy of o0Crofty0o and o0DemonBoy0o

check out my other mod(s) 
Alice Weapons - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12947
_______________________________________________________________________________

V 1.0 Female only

[s]V1.1[/s] Males eventually


Roughly 15 new eyes and variants of them for your use AND 2 new modified eyeball models FOR HUMANS.

[u]Some are really dark, but should be visible in most cases.[/u]

[b]These eyes do not mess with any other eye mods unless they change eyeball models for some reason. Lighting mods may give you undesirable results (or desirable because now you can see some of the sigils and stuff)[/b]


Some of these textures are custom.


Just Drop em in, They should be the first on the list
________________________________________________________________________________

CURRENTLY ONLY HUMAN FEMALES I DON\'T CARE IF YOU DEMAND IT FOR OTHER RACES (Kitties and Lizards), IT\'S NOT GOING TO HAPPEN; I\'LL ADD MALES LATER (and maybe elves)!


________________________________________________________________________________

Vampire eyes will overide these.

Will not mess with any replacement/adding mods for eyes

May mess with enhanced sliders and may not work with other eye models



________________________________________________________________________________


If you have an suggestions for this or other mods, please tell me on Skyrim Nexus, Deviantart (Muffinsforever), or Steam



`Forevermuffins
